%vlocity_namespace%__PropertySet__c.text: Anthem will facilitate the banking set up once the group is approved for enrollment. Also, if the group needs to sign the banking form as they elected to upload contribution files online, the group contact will now receive the email to review or add banking details to the questionnaire and eSign the document. This form is required in order to move forward with banking integration. Once the group signs, the form will be automatically returned to Anthem to be sent for banking set up once the group is approved. Notifications will be sent to the members to accept their account, and it is crucial that members do this immediately in order for them to be able to use HSA funds on qualified medical expenses. Qualified medical expenses are based on when the account is accepted and opened.
